{"id":288680,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-湖南凤凰古城商户集体罢市、集会示威抗/","date":"2013-04-11T09:15:49Z","modified":"2016-02-11T21:22:18Z","title":"维权网 | 湖南凤凰古城商户集体罢市、集会示威抗议全城收费模式  （图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>，湖南省湘西凤凰县凤凰古城商户集体罢市、集会示威，古城主要街道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">85</span><span>％以上店铺关门，从早上开始陆续有数千商户、船主、游客游行至古城北门码头集会，与政府及古城公司理论，抵制政府</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日开始启动的“全城收费”模式。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日起</span><span>，凤凰古城启动的“全城收费模式”致使古城游客骤减，引发古城所有商户、船主不满。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>集会现场有大量警员到场，集会人群中一名女子被警察殴打致满脸是血，有围观群众拍照，被便衣拉住要求删掉照片，并要抢夺手机，有围观者被警方带走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>，在湖南省凤凰县政府门前，有大量商户静坐抗议政府实行景区收费门票制。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>按照凤凰当地政府的新规定，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日起</span><span>，每一位进入湖南凤凰古城风景名胜区的游客，不论是否参观古城内的景点，都将收取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">148</span><span>元门票费。古城商户担忧这种门票制度会对客流量造成损失，一旦大量客源流失，则商铺的经营会难以为继。而有游人表示，以前在古城漫步不要钱，现在为什么进城就要收费了呢，自己只想在凤凰沱江边吹吹风，在古城里漫漫步，都要收</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">148</span><span>元门票费，不合理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-zK7Wyuuy68w/UWZrdDfAXDI/AAAAAAAAgIs/Ds-kfholpIQ/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-zK7Wyuuy68w/UWZrdDfAXDI/AAAAAAAAgIs/Ds-kfholpIQ/s400/1.jpg\" width=\"295\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Geb9SNQpsGA/UWZrevjj64I/AAAAAAAAgI0/EjS_Eso0mvs/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Geb9SNQpsGA/UWZrevjj64I/AAAAAAAAgI0/EjS_Eso0mvs/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"316\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4MQFAV739tM/UWZrg7ZSMRI/AAAAAAAAgI8/-vJt4hG_ais/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"265\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4MQFAV739tM/UWZrg7ZSMRI/AAAAAAAAgI8/-vJt4hG_ais/s400/3.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-pqPxQaGJvwI/UWZriiTrZMI/AAAAAAAAgJE/ST59yh1ZToU/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"365\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-pqPxQaGJvwI/UWZriiTrZMI/AAAAAAAAgJE/ST59yh1ZToU/s400/4.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-oK5tvzBayMo/UWZrkimyHkI/AAAAAAAAgJM/W6u8SyrjIsI/s1600/5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-oK5tvzBayMo/UWZrkimyHkI/AAAAAAAAgJM/W6u8SyrjIsI/s400/5.jpg\" width=\"298\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&amp;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a></p>\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[15021,19196,19797]}